{
  "stem": "11916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When the German come, they counting us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have to stay five in line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were quite few mother who was let stay in life, but their children had been taken from them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they was very, very sick after their children's-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] About two or three weeks later, I was taken back to another place from this barrack, to a second barrack.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And maybe with 50 numbers on this barrack, we was again looked over by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What happened with the rest, I do not know, but about 15 or so was taken back to the barracks where I was taken.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was Mengele, who was again selected the girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was taken back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, everybody questioned, what happened?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened with the others?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had no answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing-- they just don't believe they send us back, and they did not know for why.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's happened one more times-- same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the third times happened again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This time, I was sent to Reichenbach for a working place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six weeks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44, May.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] maybe the fifth days and about five to six weeks-- more six weeks than five weeks, when I was taken from Auschwitz this time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they won't take me this time, I wouldn't last much longer in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was sick, and when I went to, you know, to the washroom, blood start to come from my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] stomach.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was pretty well-- if it's starting, you'll be taken to the crematorium anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because how long could you hold on?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
